 Galvatron sent a sensor sweep and saw a gathering of warriors at a 
coordinate. he didnt know what this was but felt it may be useful to watch. 
he sent out a small probe to watch from afar to see what was going on. He 
turned to his minion. "Get in you lab and get to work on what we discussed." 
The minion bowed and hurried to his lab to work.

--part1_12d.2e6e985.28a89603_boundary
